.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
.env
.DS_Store
*.pdf
# Exception: bundled directions PDFs are committed so the Cloud Run image
# carries them. Refresh via `make sync-directions` after the skill's
# render_directions output changes.
!app/static/directions/*.pdf
/tmp/
.pytest_cache/
.ruff_cache/

# NOTE: the generated personalized templates (app/templates/bowel_prep/*-personalized.html,
# built by scripts/build_personalized_templates.py on `make vendor-sync`) are COMMITTED —
# the CI image builds from git, so they MUST be tracked. combined-print-personalized.{en,es}
# were previously ignored here, which 500'd `combined` /render on any clean-git build
# (worked locally + on deploy-from-local). Regenerated deterministically; `make vendor-check`
# guards staleness. Edit the canonical skill template, not these by hand.
